Spring JMS provider annotation based JMS ApI for send and receiving the message.
To enable the JMS in any Spring application we have to annotate SpringBootMain class with @EnableJMS
Queue information can be fetched from application properties
We have to use Spring -> JmsTemplate which provide for sending the message. Check MessageSender class
For listening the message annotate the Listener class method with @JmsListener providing the queue name
and that's it.